{"tid":804042,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[點解日本得]池江璃花子成亞運最有價值運動員","createTime":"2018-09-02T17:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-03T00:28:43.000Z","uid":179810,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d978e36d362c3c8f7236bdab0ca083e92156bb0e","tid":804042,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:13:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/533875/即時新聞/池江璃花子成亞運最有價值運動員\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F533875%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%B1%A0%E6%B1%9F%E7%92%83%E8%8A%B1%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1&d=nxtd%2Bd32wDQI7AuCi7YvBo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=eb4d96a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F533875%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%B1%A0%E6%B1%9F%E7%92%83%E8%8A%B1%E5%AD%90%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E9%81%8B%E6%9C%80%E6%9C%89%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%E5%93%A1&h=970327fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/533875/即時新聞/池江璃花子成亞運最有價值運動員</a><br />\n日本泳手池江璃花子大熱當選今屆亞運最有價值運動員。 <br />\n<br />\n池江璃花子在亞奧理事會終身名譽副主席魏紀中手中，接過最有價值運動員的獎座，並獲得五萬美元的獎金，是自獎項成立以來首位獲獎的女運動員。這位十八歲日本泳壇新星首次參加亞運便表現驚人，連取六金，成為日本史上單屆亞運贏得最多金牌的運動員，還有兩面銀牌，和刷新六項大會紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af20c6cd0e0ed38c4d298c45c0b3d622d9f9e810","tid":804042,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:36:08.000Z","msg":"東瀛泳壇「天才少女」大熱當選MVP！18歲日本泳手池江璃花子憑著紀錄性獨取6金2銀的驕人成績，打破男將過去五屆壟斷局面，成為首位榮膺亞運會最有價值運動員的女子選手。<br />\n<br />\n自1998年曼谷亞運首設MVP獎項以來，一直由男子運動員奪得殊榮，包括日本「飛人」伊藤浩二（1998年曼谷）、日本「蛙王」北島康介（2002年釜山）、韓國「海洋男孩」朴泰桓（2006年多哈）、中國羽毛球「天王」林丹（2010年廣州）及日本泳手荻野公介（2014年仁川）；直至今屆亞運會終於誕生首位亞運MVP英雌。<br />\n<br />\n現仍就讀高中的池江璃花子在雅亞達大放異彩，贏下50米蝶泳、50米自由泳、100米自由泳、100米蝶泳、4&times;100米自由泳接力及4&times;100米混合泳接力共6面金牌，並奪女子4&times;200米自由泳接力及男女4&times;100米混合泳接力兩杖銀牌，這位東京女生終以6金2銀兼刷新6項大會紀錄的佳績完成個人首次亞運之旅，亦成為歷史上單屆亞運金牌數目最多的女子運動員（相關報導：6金6紀錄改寫歷史！日本少女飛魚「預約」當MVP），前途無限。"},{"pid":"613c5af0574a2fd3ab1af377ee558e7a9366bd6f","tid":804042,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"相反韓狗攞少咗獎<br />\n仲要賴人啲嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09236c458d6cb2d956a5e8c2a59e9495449d20be","tid":804042,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"613c5af0574a2fd3ab1af377ee558e7a9366bd6f","tid":804042,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"相反韓狗攞少咗獎<br />\n仲要賴人啲嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"韓狗冇泡菜同芝士食唔慣嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45adb72d6dd18a8b1b977d52348a36b570dda40","tid":804042,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"09236c458d6cb2d956a5e8c2a59e9495449d20be","tid":804042,"uid":52006,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"613c5af0574a2fd3ab1af377ee558e7a9366bd6f","tid":804042,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:53:04.000Z","msg":"相反韓狗攞少咗獎<br />\n仲要賴人啲嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"韓狗冇泡菜同芝士食唔慣嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T17:57:31.000Z","msg":"食開屎突然冇得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5661d05215e59d7d87641f40f4bba41d3ad702","tid":804042,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T18:54:14.000Z","msg":"Skr skr skr🤙🏻🤙🏻🤙🏻🤙🏻"},{"pid":"5f9363c717cf3f83b695643979608791a1439be7","tid":804042,"uid":3194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a45adb72d6dd18a8b1b977d52348a36b570dda40","tid":804042,"uid":94828,"